Levarage: PnL according to the amount after leveraging, so not high Lev is the best. higher than 10* less than 100* is ok. 
  leverage & Margin 

进场entry、止损stop、目标goal:
  1. more use "pending order" #https://wiki.mbalib.com/wiki/%E6%8C%82%E5%8D%95%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93
  2. buy limit（下降到x价位后会向上反弹，可以在x价位做多）: eg.
                    1. mkt=1.3383 entry必须远离市价至少36点，so entry=1.3350；
                    2. stop = last📈1.3320低一点 = 1.3310；
                    3. goal = entry + （参考normal volatility range 120bps in EURUSD）= 1.3450
  2. sell limit（上升到x价位后会向下反弹，可以在x价位做空）: eg.
                    1. mkt= entry必须远离市价至少56点，so entry = rebound channel related last📈0.9147低一点 = 0.9145；
                    2. stop = last📉0.9177高一点 = 0.9185；
                    3. goal = entry -（参考normal volatility range 95bps in USDCHF）= 0.9050    
                    4. P ： L= (goal-entry) :（stop-entry) = 2:1, 有效的。         
                    
PnL:eg.
  EUR/USD: 1.2300/1.2302 ; 
  EUR/USD: 1.2400/1.2402.
      when做多: buy at 1.2302, sell at 1.2400;
      when做空: sell at 1.2300, buy at 1.2402.
      
Gold, other Currency:
  1. USDCAD: 依附USD
  2. gold: 1) most currency depreciate, gold📈; 2) CBs loose, gold📈; 3) Gold remain high and volatile
  3. EUR、GBP, CHF一致行很高；AUD与EUR有相关性；Gold与EUR，CHF相关性大，但市场risk-off时，Gold与USD，JPY相关性强。
  
 



                    

